snippet.title: Spandex Force: Champion Rising Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for the upcoming superhero puzzle RPG Spandex Force: Champion Rising, to be released for Windows and Android on April 11, with Mac and iOS versions coming later.

Visit http://www.spandexforce.com for more information and downloads!
